I"<p>As an urban art enthusiast, I was pretty happy to see a huge Os Gemeos painting as I exited South Station in Boston, MA. I was also happy to be exiting South Station.</p>

<p><img src="http://www.vincentbarr.com/assets/images/os-gemeos.png" alt="Os Gemeos" /></p>

<p>Then, I became curious about what other urban art works are popping up around Spain that I might like.</p>

